  <prompt>
    <goal>Restructure App.tsx from the current 2-panel layout to a 3-panel layout (Editor + Source + Chat) wrapped in AnalysisAiProvider, using usePanelLayout for sizing and ChatPanel for the right panel.</goal>
    <context>
      App.tsx is currently ~743 lines with a 2-panel layout (Editor + Source) and side pane launch code.
      This task adds the AnalysisAiProvider wrapper, integrates usePanelLayout for three panels, adds a second PanelSplitter, and mounts ChatPanel in the right panel.
      The legacy side pane launch code (lines 416-493 approximately) should be kept for now (Phase 1 parallel operation) but the embedded ChatPanel is the primary path.
    </context>
    <constraints>
      - MUST wrap component tree in AnalysisAiProvider
      - MUST use usePanelLayout for three-panel management
      - MUST add second PanelSplitter between Source and Chat panels
      - MUST keep existing EditorPanel and SourceViewerPanel functioning
      - MUST maintain dark mode support (FluentProvider + theme detection)
      - MUST NOT remove side pane code yet (Phase 2 task)
    </constraints>
  </prompt>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>src/client/code-pages/AnalysisWorkspace/src/App.tsx</file>
      <file>src/client/code-pages/AnalysisWorkspace/src/components/PanelSplitter.tsx</file>
      <file>src/client/code-pages/AnalysisWorkspace/src/components/EditorPanel.tsx</file>
      <file>src/client/code-pages/AnalysisWorkspace/src/components/SourceViewerPanel.tsx</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-021-fluent-design-system.md</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-026-full-page-custom-page-standard.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step>Read current App.tsx thoroughly — understand layout structure, hook usage, rendering flow</step>
    <step>Add AnalysisAiProvider as wrapper around the main content area</step>
    <step>Replace usePanelResize with usePanelLayout for three-panel management</step>
    <step>Add ChatPanel as the third (right) panel</step>
    <step>Add second PanelSplitter between Source and Chat panels</step>
    <step>Wire panel sizes from usePanelLayout to flex styles on all three panels</step>
    <step>Verify existing functionality still works (editor, source viewer, toolbar)</step>
    <step>Run build and fix any type errors</step>
  </steps>

  <outputs>
    <output>Modified: src/client/code-pages/AnalysisWorkspace/src/App.tsx</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>App.tsx renders three panels: Editor + Source + Chat</criterion>
    <criterion>AnalysisAiProvider wraps the component tree</criterion>
    <criterion>Two PanelSplitters present and draggable</criterion>
